msgid "Illustration of kurtosis"
msgstr "Illustration der Kurtosis"

#: ../../Ch04/Ch04_Descriptives_3.rst:73
msgid ""
"An illustration of kurtosis. On the left, we have a “platykurtic” "
"distribution (kurtosis = -.95) meaning that the distribution has “thin” "
"or flat tails. In the middle we have a “mesokurtic” distribution "
"(kurtosis is almost exactly 0) which means that the tails are neither "
"thin or fat. Finally, on the right, we have a “leptokurtic” distribution "
"(kurtosis = 2.12) indicating that the distribution has “fat” tails. Note "
"that kurtosis is measured with respect to a normal distribution (black "
"line)."
msgstr ""
"Eine Illustration der Kurtosis. Auf der linken Seite haben wir eine "
